It might be a little hot.

13
00:00:24,266 --> 00:00:25,266
What about mine?

14
00:00:25,433 --> 00:00:26,433
What about mine?

15
00:00:26,766 --> 00:00:27,766
You get it yourself.

16
00:00:28,566 --> 00:00:30,066
