30
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:27,466
Continue using it, okay sis?

31
00:01:28,366 --> 00:01:32,000
Where is Narin?
I haven't seen him for awile.

32
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:35,166
Ever since you two've been together,

33
